examples.en: I awoke several times during the night.
It was daylight when I awoke.
He awoke early, as was his custom.
It was midday when she awoke.
We awoke to a chorus of birdsong.
John awoke from a fitful sleep.
She awoke to the squawk of chickens.
He awoke with a painful stiffness in his neck.
When she awoke the clarity was back in her eyes.
She fell asleep immediately but awoke an hour later.
She awoke to the steady pitter-patter of raindrops tingling on the rooftop.
